scene_description_enriched: A ram stands in profile, facing right, amidst foliage. The ram has prominent, curled horns and its body is depicted with stylized lines. The background is filled with a dense pattern of dots, suggesting a starry sky or a textured surface. The scene is framed by an arched border with decorative elements. The ram is a symbol of Christ's sacrifice, particularly in the context of the Passover lamb, and can also represent the zodiac sign Aries.
